化纤钛白常规包装每袋净重25kg或500kg带托盘吨包装。<br>\n**运输：**化纤钛白的运输必须保持干燥、严防雨淋，不得与可能使产品变质或使包装损坏的物品混运，应保证产品的安全和包装清洁。<br>\n**贮存：**化纤钛白的贮存应保持干燥、通风、避光，尽量在室内或带遮蓬的场所，应保持贮存场所的清洁，防止日晒，严防潮湿和雨淋。有效期限从生产日期起为三年，超过有效日期时须对全项目进行复验，复验合格方能使用。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/uploads/1966_0375d8894c.png\" alt=\"1966.png\"></p>"}}},"title":"1966化学纤维用二氧化钛","time":null,"description":"长纤专用化纤级二氧化钛：产品是采用国际上通常的生产方法，在水箱中通过对二氧化钛颗粒表面进行包覆改性，以降低其光敏性及提高它的分散性。表面包覆均匀，产品性能稳定等优点。适用于高品质的涤纶、长纤和要求高的化纤色母粒等。  ","keywords":"1966化学纤维用二氧化钛、长纤专用化纤级二氧化钛","image":{"localFile":{"publicURL":"/static/4538f15a92cfa9bf367e65f319c634a5/Fh_DQ_Dm_Kb_Dmy_s_A_Mdy_K_Cu2_EL_2nl3_K_42e2de46d5.png","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#989898","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/4538f15a92cfa9bf367e65f319c634a5/4576d/Fh_DQ_Dm_Kb_Dmy_s_A_Mdy_K_Cu2_EL_2nl3_K_42e2de46d5.png","srcSet":"/static/4538f15a92cfa9bf367e65f319c634a5/6addd/Fh_DQ_Dm_Kb_Dmy_s_A_Mdy_K_Cu2_EL_2nl3_K_42e2de46d5.png 400w,\n/static/4538f15a92cfa9bf367e65f319c634a5/c2d17/Fh_DQ_Dm_Kb_Dmy_s_A_Mdy_K_Cu2_EL_2nl3_K_42e2de46d5.png 800w,\n/static/4538f15a92cfa9bf367e65f319c634a5/4576d/Fh_DQ_Dm_Kb_Dmy_s_A_Mdy_K_Cu2_EL_2nl3_K_42e2de46d5.png 1600w","sizes":"(min-width: 1600px) 1600px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/4538f15a92cfa9bf367e65f319c634a5/f5c71/Fh_DQ_Dm_Kb_Dmy_s_A_Mdy_K_Cu2_EL_2nl3_K_42e2de46d5.webp 400w,\n/static/4538f15a92cfa9bf367e65f319c634a5/0d27e/Fh_DQ_Dm_Kb_Dmy_s_A_Mdy_K_Cu2_EL_2nl3_K_42e2de46d5.webp 800w,\n/static/4538f15a92cfa9bf367e65f319c634a5/b924f/Fh_DQ_Dm_Kb_Dmy_s_A_Mdy_K_Cu2_EL_2nl3_K_42e2de46d5.webp 1600w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1600px) 1600px, 100vw"}]},"width":1600,"height":1200}}}}}},"pageContext":{"id":"3b300bbe-3bfb-5766-a100-7f2d00644be6","title":"1966化学纤维用二氧化钛"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1449321610","262846975","2711010679","329982926","3433418328","4164267127","4197482012","59985977","83641247"],"slicesMap":{}}